{"tid":1864961,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思］幫大陸人消毒嘅方法","createTime":"2020-02-06T02:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T02:25:36.000Z","uid":109631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54efe26f1ba19a52d3b96f62d25f73f898842280","tid":1864961,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"呢2日會有<strong>大量</strong>大陸人返香港<br />\n尤其係革大西營盤同暴大大埔<br />\n仲有黃埔紅磡嗰啲<br />\n雖然轉咗online teaching 但8號開始隔14日<br />\n身邊好多nds都立即改早返嚟<br />\n就會住喺大家屋企隔離仲要出出入入<br />\n佢哋係死都唔會自我隔離<br />\n只會一齊出去同你爭口罩<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以幫我哋嘅污糟鄰居右好好消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己地區自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bd1aec119e0a11172867b66a3b0e755aced0cf","tid":1864961,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:16:06.000Z","msg":"私了吧"},{"pid":"deb7d4b8e3137e25bc6a69378448f745db114661","tid":1864961,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf047b78676dea4e62c4abc8987df2449f900ec","tid":1864961,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:16:54.000Z","msg":"叫朱恒 周瑜 用火攻"},{"pid":"05bde488dbe02a551ba86c406bcbb88fbe1fe099","tid":1864961,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"如果可以有同區議員合作嘅樓層消毒就最好<br />\n<br />\n但首先要知道佢哋住邊先<br />\n唔洗好detail，始終係私隱<br />\n知咩大廈幾多樓<br />\n<br />\n有人知道嘅可以share 吓出嚟<br />\n叫大家小心<br />\n仲要Forward 埋比大廈法團同議員"},{"pid":"a043cdaadb75b095e9c25d4be07eb61d62cb19c3","tid":1864961,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"火燒連環船<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}